    <abstract>
      <t>This RFC argues that mobile network tracing provides both tools to improve our understanding of wireless channels, as well as to build realistic, repeatable testbeds for mobile software and systems.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.
	 </t>
